---
import SectionHighlight from "@/components/SectionHighlight.astro";


---
<div class="section-y_padding-lg bg-custom-bg-gray caret-transparent w-screen flex justify-center items-center">
    <div
      class={`grid lg:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 lg:grid-rows-12 custom-section-width text-start`}
    >
    <!--Add self-start self-center -->
      <h3 class="lg:justify-start flex justify-center items-end  lg:self-auto  col-start-1 col-span-1 lg:row-span-3  font-normal text-base">
        <SectionHighlight>Our Story</SectionHighlight>
      </h3>
      <h1 class="lg:rounded-0 lg:self-auto lg:text-start text-center leading-15 col-start-1 col-span-1 lg:row-start-4  lg:row-span-1  font-medium text-5xl">
        About VoyageBlur
      </h1>
      <div class="relative lg:aspect-auto lg:col-start-2 lg:h-[1000px] lg:row-span-12 lg:ml-[50px] lg:rounded-0 lg:mt-0 aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mt-10 col-span-1">
        <img
          loading="lazy"
          src="https://imagedelivery.net/Ap_RIQMnvK_LYOq1vIFisQ/8c44225d-6823-448d-63ef-6ac039cbc200/hd1920x1080"
          alt="Our Story Image"
          style={{ objectFit: "cover" }}
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="lg:self-start self-end text-start col-start-1 col-span-1 lg:row-start-5  lg:row-span-8 lg:mt-5 mt-10 pt-2 lg:pr-[50px] font-normal text-base text-custom-font-gray leading-[150%]">
        Founded in 2025, VoyageBlur was born from a passion for capturing the
        world through the unique aesthetics of analog film. In a digital age,
        we believe there&apos;s something magical about the imperfect, tangible
        nature of film photography.<br/>
        <span class="inline-block mt-5 w-full" />
        Our mission is to document travel
        experiences with authenticity and character that only analog formats
        can provide. Each grain, light leak, and imperfection tells part of
        the journey&apos;s story. <br/>
        <span class="inline-block mt-5 w-full"/>
        We believe that travel isn&apos;t just about visiting
        placesâ€”it&apos;s about experiencing them deeply, slowly, and thoughtfully.
        Just like the deliberate process of shooting film forces you to slow
        down and consider each frame.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>